<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٧ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«يَظْلَلْنَ، مَحْظُوراً»</span> مَعَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«المُحْتَظِرِ»</span> … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كُنْتَ فَظّاً»</span> وَجَمِيعَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«النَّظَرِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٨ - إِلَّا بِـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«وَيْلٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«هَلْ»</span> وَأُولَى <span style="color:#6c6c00">«نَاضِرَهْ»</span> … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الغَيْظُ»</span> لَا الرَّعْدُ وَهُودٌ؛ قَاصِرَهْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٥٩ - وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الحَظُّ»</span> لَا <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الحَضُّ عَلَى الطَّعَامِ»</span> … وَفِي <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ظَنِينٍ»</span>: الخِلَافُ سَامِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
